works.description: Renowned Swiss watchmaker Franck Muller, who presented the world’s largest tourbillon ever incorporated into a wristwatch during Baselworld 2011, has celebrated its 20th anniversary with a special series of iPhone 4 cases. These special edition iPhone 4 cases made of titanium are available through Beams in Japan. These cases take in the theme of time and flaunt an interconnecting digit motif throughout. There are six options to choose from, including three in tonal colors, one in a two-tone
